Note: For operations other than GET, authentication is required either by adding the credentials to
an authentication header or to an json object attached to the request.

base-api-url = <server-url>/api/<api-version>/apps

REST API endpoints:
Imported files:
    base-imported = <base-api-url>/imported
        Methods allowed:
            GET - will return a list of imported files

    imported-database = <base-imported>/<file-name>
        Methods allowed:
            GET - will return a list of root nodes from <file-name>, if database is valid

    <imported-database>/<item-id>
        Methods allowed:
            GET - will return the item with the specified id, from the specified database

    <imported-database>/<item-id>/children
        Methods: allowed:
            GET - will return the the list of direct children of the item with the specified id
